WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:900000,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:00:13.972 --> 00:00:15.432 position:50% align:center
- The Gourmet Festival
was supposed

00:00:15.515 --> 00:00:17.267 position:50% align:center
to be a fun holiday event.

00:00:18.309 --> 00:00:20.395 position:50% align:center
So why couldn't
Hazard Cast predict

00:00:20.478 --> 00:00:21.938 position:50% align:center
the sudden tornado
which tore through

00:00:22.022 --> 00:00:23.565 position:50% align:center
the GourFes venue?

00:00:23.648 --> 00:00:26.109 position:50% align:center
- A giant twister came rolling
in from the ocean.

00:00:26.192 --> 00:00:28.486 position:50% align:center
I had to do everything I could
to escape!

00:00:28.570 --> 00:00:31.573 position:50% align:center
- This unforeseen catastrophe
has resulted in 12 casualties

00:00:31.656 --> 00:00:33.283 position:50% align:center
and 36 wounded.

00:00:33.366 --> 00:00:35.452 position:50% align:center
It's been three days since
the disaster

00:00:35.535 --> 00:00:37.912 position:50% align:center
and memorial services
for Gourmet Festival victims

00:00:37.996 --> 00:00:39.998 position:50% align:center
are now taking place.

00:00:40.081 --> 00:00:42.459 position:50% align:center
Many of them are being held
in the funeral home

00:00:42.542 --> 00:00:45.462 position:50% align:center
that is located in Shiotsuki
of the 24th ward.

00:00:45.545 --> 00:00:48.256 position:50% align:center
We interviewed Mayor Gori Suido
as he was leaving one

00:00:48.340 --> 00:00:49.257 position:50% align:center
of the funerals.

00:00:49.341 --> 00:00:50.592 position:50% align:center
- Mr. Mayor.

00:00:50.675 --> 00:00:51.926 position:50% align:center
- What are your thoughts
on this tragedy?

00:00:52.010 --> 00:00:53.094 position:50% align:center
- There's a rumor
going around that

00:00:53.178 --> 00:00:54.429 position:50% align:center
the Hazard Cast
warning notification

00:00:54.512 --> 00:00:56.931 position:50% align:center
was delayed.
Is this true?

00:00:57.015 --> 00:00:59.851 position:50% align:center
- This was simply due
to a lack of cumulative data,

00:00:59.934 --> 00:01:02.771 position:50% align:center
so we will be taking measures
to gather even more data.

00:01:02.854 --> 00:01:04.689 position:50% align:center
This will start as soon
as possible.

00:01:04.773 --> 00:01:06.066 position:50% align:center
- What about
every network within

00:01:06.149 --> 00:01:07.942 position:50% align:center
the 24th ward getting hacked?

00:01:08.026 --> 00:01:10.403 position:50% align:center
- My name is Carneades.

00:01:10.487 --> 00:01:12.489 position:50% align:center
I am the one who
will thrust choices

00:01:12.572 --> 00:01:14.908 position:50% align:center
for the future at the world.

00:01:14.991 --> 00:01:18.078 position:50% align:center
- It's been several days since
we witnessed this shocking hack,

00:01:18.161 --> 00:01:19.496 position:50% align:center
but there has been
no further statement

00:01:19.579 --> 00:01:20.663 position:50% align:center
from the culprit at large.

00:01:20.747 --> 00:01:22.332 position:50% align:center
- Correct,
and as a result,

00:01:22.415 --> 00:01:24.125 position:50% align:center
most people believe
it was merely a prank

00:01:24.209 --> 00:01:25.543 position:50% align:center
by an overseas hacker group.

00:01:25.627 --> 00:01:27.170 position:50% align:center
- Perhaps, professor,

00:01:27.253 --> 00:01:29.172 position:50% align:center
but there are fringe theories
out there claiming

00:01:29.255 --> 00:01:31.466 position:50% align:center
this Carneades may
have caused that tornado.

00:01:31.549 --> 00:01:32.759 position:50% align:center
[rain pattering]
- One of the members

00:01:32.842 --> 00:01:35.220 position:50% align:center
of the DoRed crew found these
this morning.

00:01:35.303 --> 00:01:38.223 position:50% align:center
A Nijimi Station turnstile
and at the foot of Peace Bridge.

00:01:38.306 --> 00:01:41.393 position:50% align:center
- The mark we saw show up on TV?
- Yeah.

00:01:41.476 --> 00:01:43.353 position:50% align:center
I guess this'd be
that guy's tag.

00:01:43.436 --> 00:01:45.689 position:50% align:center
I wonder if he's
a street artist.

00:01:45.772 --> 00:01:48.316 position:50% align:center
- Wait, where'd you say
he graffitid the image?

00:01:48.400 --> 00:01:50.110 position:50% align:center
- Exactly.
That's the thing.

00:01:50.193 --> 00:01:52.654 position:50% align:center
Both are in the locations
we saw in visions.

00:01:52.737 --> 00:01:54.489 position:50% align:center
- Yeah, which means
this guy knows

00:01:54.572 --> 00:01:56.199 position:50% align:center
about those trolley dilemmas.

00:01:56.282 --> 00:01:58.576 position:50% align:center
If we do believe
his declaration,

00:01:58.660 --> 00:02:00.620 position:50% align:center
the dilemmas must
have been prepared by--

00:02:00.704 --> 00:02:02.414 position:50% align:center
- You mean--
- Stop this. Enough.

00:02:02.497 --> 00:02:04.708 position:50% align:center
- But Shu--
- It's all our fault, you guys.

00:02:04.791 --> 00:02:05.792 position:50% align:center
- [exhales]
- If we were able

00:02:05.875 --> 00:02:07.752 position:50% align:center
to handle things well...

00:02:07.836 --> 00:02:09.379 position:50% align:center
Dammit.

00:02:09.462 --> 00:02:12.382 position:50% align:center
If we didn't get carried away,
made better decisions,

00:02:12.465 --> 00:02:14.467 position:50% align:center
someone else could
have saved more people.

00:02:14.551 --> 00:02:16.052 position:50% align:center
- There isn't anyone else.
- Huh?

00:02:16.136 --> 00:02:19.389 position:50% align:center
- These dilemmas aren't given
to anybody other than us, right?

00:02:19.472 --> 00:02:21.683 position:50% align:center
- Let's start poking around
based on what we know.

00:02:21.766 --> 00:02:22.851 position:50% align:center
- Agreed.

00:02:22.934 --> 00:02:24.978 position:50% align:center
So, both of you,

00:02:25.061 --> 00:02:27.063 position:50% align:center
we should meet up if we get
a call from Asumi.

00:02:27.147 --> 00:02:29.190 position:50% align:center
- Sounds like a plan.
- Sure.

